1.1.name: wordpress/tab-slide
1.1.description: Slide your target page into and out of the visible page with this very useful side tab. The pages can contain forms, widgets, videos, pictures, posts, menu options, comments, logins, sign-ups, annoying popoup ads etc...There are a few templates included to get you started. The settings page appears in the Dashboard where you can set all your tab slide options such as page source, size, positioning, autohide, opacity. This plugin is ideal for users who would like to add additional content without cluttering up or leaving the page.
